quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  79,27,Mbela ko tagde mon ɓuri sattude wolla ko kammu mbo O mahi o
  79,28,O ɓamti mbildi mammbo O fotndi mbo
  79,29,O niɓɓaɗini jemma makko O yaltini annoore makko
  79,30,E leydi ndi caggal ɗuum O werti ndi. @Corrected
  79,31,O yaltini heen ndiyam mayri e durngol mayri
  79,32,Pelle ɗe O ñiɓi ɗe
  79,33,Ngam wona nafoore mon e kulle mon
  79,34,Si wuttaandu ɗimmuru ndu arii
  79,35,ñalawma mbo kala aade siftori ko o yahnoo
  79,36,Yiite nge ɓannginane wonande oon ji*oowo
  79,37,Tawi ko oon bewɗo
  79,38,O ɓurni nguurndam aduna
  79,39,Ko yiite woni hoɗorde makko
  79,40,Tawi ko oon kulɗo daraade e yeeso joom makko o haɗi fittaandu belaaɗe
  79,41,Ko aljanna woni hoɗorde makko
  79,42,Hoɓe naaamna Ma ndey darnga daroto
  79,43,A alanah ɗum ganndal saka kaala ɗum
  79,44,Ko e joom ma tan woni haaɗtirde ganndal darnga
  79,45,Ngonɗa tan ko jeertinoowo wonande kulɗo mbo
  79,46,Elle kamɓe ñande ɓe nji*ata darnga ɓe ñiiɓaani si wonah kikiiɗa yel wolla feññaange